ffe04719501c"],

Cell["\<\
The disjoint  diagrams at second order are 72 in total. These are distributed \
as follows:
i) 8 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in the antidiagonal;
ii) 8 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in the diagonal;
iii) 8 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in both the diagonal and the antidiagonal;
iv) 8 Direct diagrams dressed in the left propagator;
v) 8 Direct diagrams dressed in the right propagator;
vi) 8 Direct diagrams dressed in both the left and the right propagator;
vii) 8 Exchange diagrams dressed in the propagator above;
viii) 8 Exchange diagrams dressed in the propagator below;
ix) 8 Exchange diagrams dressed in both the above and below propagator;\
