d26553c08c17"],

Cell["\<\
Exchange diagrams with unperturbed 1-body propagators above and below are \
processed. Their initial number is 8 in total.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8836813753146152`*^9, 3.88368147043666*^9}, {
   3.8836820487185183`*^9, 3.88368205024879*^9}, {3.883682180609577*^9, 
