  3.912328458319582*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"42b134aa-c71f-4c80-9866-\
f467d20d20c2"],

Cell["\<\
Bogoliubov diagrams with unperturbed 1-body propagator on the antidiagonal \
are processed. Their initial number is 8 in total.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8836813753146152`*^9, 3.88368147043666*^9}, {
  3.8836820487185183`*^9, 3.88368205024879*^9}, {3.883682180609577*^9, 
  3.883682181425793*^9}, {3.8895326177197933`*^9, 3.8895326190004883`*^9}, {
  3.8927832371377015`*^9, 3.892783237556256*^9}, {3.911906600155179*^9, 
  3.911906604269761*^9}, {3.912324076983011*^9, 3.912324077222091*^9}, {
  3.9123286301889176`*^9, 
  3.9123286414560614`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"6359a208-168d-4b6d-9854-\
c77b3927373b"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Diagonally-dressed disjoint Bogoliubov diagrams with non-identical one-body \
vertices\
\>", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9123225301750393`*^9, 3.9123225545237913`*^9}, {
  3.9123286967354116`*^9, 3.9123287107977743`*^9}, {3.9123287715426073`*^9, 
  3.9123287814673014`*^9}, {3.9123311754152274`*^9, 
  3.9123312085869613`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f1f02c4c-9225-4466-ba86-\
431f9d618563"],

Cell["\<\
Depending on the components of the one-body potential into play, symmetry \
rules may apply and reduce the total number of fully-contracted terms. When \
the multiplied Nambu components of the one-body potential are distinct, no \
vertex exchange is possible. Additionally, since single-particle index \
transpositions within each one-body vertex are forbidden, no filtration \
process is necessary. Thus, the number of inequivalent diagonally-dressed \
disjoint Bogoliubov contributions with non-identical vertices at second order \
remains equal to 8.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.912322579269453*^9, 3.9123226345921354`*^9}, {
  3.9123226697432995`*^9, 3.9123228694040194`*^9}, {3.912323377321495*^9, 
  3.9123233835289555`*^9}, {3.9123331180668077`*^9, 3.912333133784379*^9}, {
  3.9123337248637705`*^9, 3.912333725851756*^9}, {3.912334200112067*^9, 
  3.912334205774393*^9}, {3.912334269934724*^9, 3.9123342744885716`*^9}, {
  3.912334370889967*^9, 3.9123343803464336`*^9}, {3.912334773333669*^9, 
  3.912334773850529*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8ee827a1-54fb-4dff-8f83-\
d56ed235e682"],

