Cell["\<\
There are only 8 inequivalent second-order \
diagonally-and-antidiagonally-dressed disjoint Bogoliubov diagrams with \
identical one-body vertices. The multiplicity check is fulfilled.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8895308415440407`*^9, 3.889530867561658*^9}, {
